{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"aa5178e3f0","title":"童小鹏与北京政法学院红卫兵座谈纪要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9bc31d698c","index":0,"year":1966,"month":10,"day":20,"articleId":"aa5178e3f0"}],"tags":[{"id":"3dc1cfb1b8","name":"童小鹏","type":"人物"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dbcf15bd08","name":"陶铸","type":"人物"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"14279e90fc","name":"童小鹏"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6e87892af4","type":"title","text":"童小鹏与北京政法学院红卫兵座谈纪要","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aa5178e3f0"},{"id":"88e6a18777","type":"authors","text":"童小鹏","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aa5178e3f0"},{"id":"4d950581ed","type":"appellation","text":"〖时间：晚〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aa5178e3f0"},{"id":"5d1d03a7c9","type":"paragraph","text":"一、关于修正主义红卫兵？","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aa5178e3f0"},{"id":"d81b497be1","type":"paragraph","text":"童说：今天我见有人问陈伯达同志这个问题，陈伯达同志说：“修正主义红卫兵不是指哪一个红卫兵组织，指的是红卫兵的个别人，如执行资产阶级反动路线的主力、谭力夫。”","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aa5178e3f0"},{"id":"f702c80c38","type":"paragraph","text":"有人问：“中央领导人几次不接见我们，是不是因为我们是修正主义红卫兵？”","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aa5178e3f0"},{"id":"c313b9674f","type":"paragraph","text":"童答：“不是，林彪同志、周总理在天安门上讲了，一切红卫兵组织都是革命组织。”","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aa5178e3f0"},{"id":"72f84fe288","type":"paragraph","text":"有人问：“林彪同志、周总理的讲话现在是否还有效？”","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aa5178e3f0"},{"id":"46236a7e8c","type":"paragraph","text":"童答：“完全有效，林彪同志、周总理的讲话是代表党中央和毛主席的。”","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aa5178e3f0"},{"id":"04fbf76f24","type":"paragraph","text":"二、关于传说“江青同志对别人讲毛主席在中央是少数的问题。”","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aa5178e3f0"},{"id":"5f8bf1ff99","type":"paragraph","text":"童说：“那是谣言，总理在昨天已澄清了。”张春桥说“江青同志讲的是几十年前国民党时期文艺界的事，那时主席和江青同志是少数。”","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aa5178e3f0"},{"id":"03c1243fc9","type":"paragraph","text":"孙同志说：“从遵义会议起，毛主席在中央一直是多数，威望很高，不仅那时是，现在也是，将来仍然是。”","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aa5178e3f0"},{"id":"3bac593b30","type":"paragraph","text":"三、关于“怀疑一切”的问题？","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aa5178e3f0"},{"id":"24034c64ab","type":"paragraph","text":"童说：“有人提‘怀疑一切’的口号，陶铸同志听了说：‘毛主席能怀疑吗？林彪同志能怀疑吗？’陶铸同志讲话的前提是不能怀疑一切，被人误传为除了毛主席和林彪同志外都可以怀疑，这样意思就改变了。”","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aa5178e3f0"}],"page":{"id":"66e30b6ed3","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aa5178e3f0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}